reviews_data.review_text: Best coffee in Cabarrus County. Great staff
Verb coffee Multiply is amazing. They have the best baristas. so nice and so sweet.

Great coffee and wonderful service.
Friendly and helpful.
Great atmosphere. A great place to visit.
mya was so nice! awesome coffee
Maya at Verb Cocord was great! The coffee is simple but eloquent and crafted with care. Love it.
Maya serviced me today and she was very sweet!
They were really nice and the drink was amazing.
IMO, this is Concord’s best coffee.  I attend Multiply church and love the location.  Very convenient and the seating area is a great place to work.
Verb has by far the best most consistent coffee in Concord. It has such a welcoming environment and the kindest staff!
Always pleasant
Mya is so friendly and served up a great macha
Coffee and pastries are phenomenal 🙌🏻
coffee is always consistently good , staff is always so nice and helpful . If you want good quality tasting espresso and beans highly recommend for concord area !
So happy to have a second Verb location!!
